data.description: Welcome to the epitome of potential! This 4-bed, 2-bath residence spanning 2,273 sqft is more than a home – it's an opportunity waiting for your personal touch. Nestled in a prime location, this property caters to both investors and those with an eye for value. Imagine the transformation with just a dash of paint and minor drywall enhancements. Boasting a conservative ARV of $340,000 and showcasing new roof, A/C, and plumbing, this isn't just a house; it's a canvas for your dreams. Priced to sell quickly, don't miss out on the chance to shape this space into your perfect haven. Act now, as opportunities like this are rare – schedule your showing and let your vision unfold!
